message.text:
⚡ Heads Up! ⚡
Tams FX is still searching for passionate Executive Committee members and competitive Esports players!
We’re giving you more time—applications are now open until September 16! ⏳
A new journey awaits. Are you ready to take the challenge? 🎮🔥

Apply now through the links below:

Executive Committee:
https://forms.office.com/r/FBEEb8v9nH

Esports:
https://forms.office.com/r/eQi7vxvTAd

Check the FAQs part of this link for general inquiries:
https://tinyurl.com/TFXTamHunt25

You can also message the page for inquries and our staff will be attending to your concerns once available.

Co-presented by:
- Val Collections
- Drip and Bites
- Ryzzia Joy de Torres

#SeekingTheUnknownTogether
#TFXUnleashed  

Illustrations by: Ash Raymundo & Royce Bitoy
Caption by: Shawn Watchorna
